title: Hotel Check-In
description:
Jared Carrabis unofficially departs Barstool Sports for DraftKings (00:00:30). Jim Braude & Margery Eagan call Moss from Dudley "a chicken" (00:28:30). Chris is worried about gas prices (00:48:00). ESPN deletes portions of Jeff Passan's appearance on their daily podcast (00:54:30). Falcons Wide Receiver Calvin Ridley suspended for the 2022 season over gambling (00:58:00). A Michigan house candidate says he tells daughters, "if rape is inevitable then sit back and enjoy it" (01:04:00). Hotel check-in preparation, calls & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
